<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/11(Thu) A day-tour in Ching-jing Farm/ Taiwanese Traditional Wedding (Host: Leroy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=642&amp;p=667#p667"><![CDATA[
A day-tour in Ching-jing Farm/ Taiwanese Traditional Wedding (Host: Leroy)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1: A day-tour in Ching-jing Farm<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pewbu1dEKfY">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pewbu1dEKfY</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=st7lSoxSc6c">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=st7lSoxSc6c</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QM2yM4KVqc0">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QM2yM4KVqc0</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />How many scenic spots do you know in Taiwan, such as Cingjing Farm?<br /><br />1、What are your most recommended tourist attractions in the mountains of Taiwan?<br /><br />2、What are your most recommended tourist attractions on the seaside or coast of Taiwan?<br /><br />3、Which of the cities in Taiwan is your most recommended tourist city?<br /><br />4、If you have a three-day vacation, what plan would you recommend?<br /><br /><br />Session 2: Taiwanese Traditional Wedding <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4UOsDxF1TI">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4UOsDxF1TI</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />How much do you know about Taiwan's wedding and funeral culture?<br /><br />1、Do you know the ceremony or process of getting married in Taiwan? Can you share?<br /><br />2、If there is a funeral at home, what are the taboos not to do? Can you share it?<br /><br />3、How do you usually celebrate a happy event at home, such as an elder’s birthday, a child’s full moon, or a family passing a national exam？<br /><br />4、Can you share the calendar of Taiwanese folk festivals you know, such as Mazu's circumnavigation or local temple fairs, etc.<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Aug 05, 2022 4:06 pm</p><hr />
